  "description": "High pulse rate (2.0 Hz) with minimal entrainment (0.05) — the 6 Kuramoto oscillators run at independent natural frequencies, creating polyrhythmic pulse interference. Unknot state keeps the FDN clean so only the pulse patterns are heard. LFO1 at 1.5 Hz square-waves the tangle for rhythmic gating.",
